  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 492a1892d85284c9abfa8dd9fa064be4, type: 3}
  m_Name: Slide_06_EndParries
  m_EditorClassIdentifier:
  title: "They Learn Too"
  body: "Enemies can parry your attacks. After deflecting enough strikes, they\u2019ll
    launch a counter-attack \u2014 signaled by the end-parry.\n\nWatch for the tell.
    When an enemy parries your combo, be ready to switch to defense immediately.
    Reckless aggression gets punished."
